overview.en: UNDT (Union Network Dollar Token) is an encrypted currency with price stability. It is linked to the value of US dollar and issued by pledging stable currency assets under UNIONDAO agreement.
overview.zh: UNDT（Union Network Dollar Token）是一种具有价格稳定特性的加密货币，与美元价值挂钩，在UNIONDAO协议下通过质押稳定币资产而发行。
